* 山姆小鎮 Sam's Town (2006)
* 歲月 Day & Age (2008)
* 光榮戰役 Battle Born (2012)
* 完美境界 Wonderful Wonderful (2017)
* 幻想爆發 Imploding The Mirage (2020)
* Pressure Machine (2021)

